body_html:
I was confused myself... and happened to come across this old issue searching about TF_SessionRun.

It seems TF_Output could have been called TF_OperationValue to choose a neutral name for the type, and then input/outputs are terms relative to TF_SessionRun.

Just thought I'd share, even though this has been long closed.
